descriptionHtml:
Athene was the most powerful two-handed axe warrior in Tamriel.
As a nord, Athene was a true believer of talos. She was sentenced to life imprisonment for it  and put in Helgen jail. She was so angry that the thunder and bloodlust exploded. One day, a huge drangon named Alduin razed the  Helgen, she escaped from prison to the Riverwood. The town was  beautiful, and everyone was amiable and free , which was the life she wanted. Athene heard Whiterun lord could tolerate the nagging Heimskr to deliver sermons about Talos and the town of Riverwood was Whiterun territory, so she decided to stay and help the town assault against bandits, vampires and dragon.

Body:UNP  
Level:2-300（1.2rate）
Location: Sleeping Giant Inn
Voice:Female Young Eager
Height/weight:1.0/100
Combatstyle :preferring heavy armor and two-handed Axe,  crossbow.
